==车站周边==
30街車站位于连接费城市中心和大学城的市场街[[斯库尔基尔河|思故河]]畔，因此成为连接河两岸的桥头堡。由于距离市区较近，车站周围大部分为较高密度建筑，主要为办公写字楼，大部分均属于[[卓克索大學|卓克索大學]]<ref name="drexel-map">{{cite web | url=http://www.drexel.edu/em/directions/map_uc.pdf | title=University City Main Campus | accessdate=2009-06-05 | date=2008-12-16 | publisher=Drexel University | format=PDF; 1,3 MB| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922235909/http://www.drexel.edu/em/directions/map_uc.pdf| archivedate=2010-09-22}}</ref>。

市场街对侧为原[[美國郵政署|美國郵政署]]的{{link-en|美国邮政署分支大楼 (费城)|United States Post Office-Main Branch (Philadelphia, Pennsylvania)|邮件分拣大楼}}，该建筑风格与30街车站站房类似，建于1930年，覆盖地面站场南侧<ref name="Kyr-3f">{{cite url|author=Kyriakodis, Harry|url=http://www.prrths.com/Downloads/Philly's~Subways~Railways~and~Stations1.pdf|archive-date=2011-09-19|title=The Subways, Railways and Stations of Philly: Written Material to Accompany a Mostly-Underground Tour from 30th Street Station to Market East Station|publisher=The Pennsylvania Railroad Technical and Historical Society|year=2007|access-date=2022-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110919210137/http://www.prrths.com/Downloads/Philly%27s~Subways~Railways~and~Stations1.pdf}}</ref>，2010年改建为办公楼。

2004-2005年在车站北侧旁建成上盖物业{{link-en|希拉中心|Cira Centre}}，为133米高、29层的写字楼，和车站站房通过天桥连接。该大厦是费城思故河西岸第一座高层建筑<ref>Emporis: ''[http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/bu/?id=149009 Cira Centre] {{Wayback|url=http://www.emporis.com/en/wm/bu/?id=149009 |date=20070410223354 }}''.</ref>。2013年起在原邮局南侧又开建上盖物业{{link-en|希拉中心南|Cira Centre South}}，设有一座33层430英尺（131米）高的公寓大楼Evo和一座一座49层、730英尺（223米）高的商住大楼FMC Tower<ref>{{cite web | title=EVO {{!}} Campus Crest | url=http://campuscrest.com/student-housing/evo/ | url-status=dead | publisher=Campus Crest | location=North Carolina, United States | accessdate=14 September 2013 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130910211406/http://campuscrest.com/student-housing/evo/ | archivedate=10 September 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://forum.skyscraperpage.com/showthread.php?t=137163 | title=PHILADELPHIA {{!}} EVO @ Cira Centre South {{!}} 407 FT {{!}} 33 FLRS {{!}} U/C | website=[[SkyscraperPage|SkyscraperPage]] | format=blog | date=1 September 2007<!--date of last posting to thread--> | access-date=2021-07-13 | archive-date=2019-12-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204071141/http://forum.skyscraperpage.com/showthread.php?t=137163 }}</ref><ref name="Grove">{{cite web|title=Grove at Cira Centre South|url=http://www.facilities.upenn.edu/maps/locations/grove-cira-centre-south|publisher=University of Pennsylvania Facilities & Real Estate Services|accessdate=20 August 2013|archive-date=2018-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624175738/https://www.facilities.upenn.edu/maps/locations/grove-cira-centre-south}}</ref>，分别于2014年和2016年建成。

==接驳交通==
费城地铁[[市场-法兰克福线|市场-法兰克福线]]（蓝线），[[SEPTA|SEPTA]]有轨电车10，11，13，36路。地铁与有轨电车在同名地下站{{link-en|三十街车站 (地铁)|30th Street station (SEPTA subway)|三十街车站}}内，位于30街火车站前、市场街地下。该地铁车站和铁路站房原由地道连接，但该地道于1980年代因安全原因封闭。美铁和SEPTA原计划于2000年代重开该地道，但后因[[九一一事件|九一一事件]]而告吹<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.inquirer.com/philly/columnists/inga_saffron/Archive_Subway_riders_get_shortchanged_at_30th_St_Station.html |title=Archive: Subway riders get shortchanged at 30th St. Station |last=Saffron |first=Inga |date=March 7, 2003 |work=[[The_Philadelphia_Inquirer|The Philadelphia Inquirer]] |access-date=May 31, 2020 |archive-date=2021-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210717011709/https://www.inquirer.com/philly/columnists/inga_saffron/Archive_Subway_riders_get_shortchanged_at_30th_St_Station.html }}</ref>。

